   Instantly causes the argument of this command to be killed
   Useful for destroying a mob or player without the hassle of 
   fighting it.  Things slain will yield a corpse complete with 
   equipment and gold, but will yield no xp to the slayer nor
   will PC's lose any xp by being slain.

  "kill" and "slay" are synonymous.  If you wish to fight, use hit.
